
Virtual environments:

python environment which libraries, modules or scripts
that are isolated form system.
dependencies to separated to prevent version conflicts
quick module deletion upon completion

web framework - back end development
micro framework - lacks tools by default
used by netflix reddit linkedin etc

lightweight, simple to implement, highly customisable, good doc, python in webdev

Makes flask run:
app = Flask(__name__)

if __name__ == "__main__":
    app.run(debug=True, port=8000)




